{"tid":1780376,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人不是中國人 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-12-12T10:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:56:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"292111d48c0195a09d1bc09195434128756f50ad","tid":1780376,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191212/20823390/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F20823390%2F&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=52667a32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F20823390%2F&h=530ee5cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191212/20823390/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人不是中國人 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191212/large/1576048554_bc25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191212%2Flarge%2F1576048554_bc25.jpg&h=aee58d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電視截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東亞足球錦標賽首戰，中國隊1:2輸給日本隊。輸波事小，輸品事大。上半場30分鐘，中國球員姜至鵬在截波時，左腳高舉，直接踹向日本門將橋岡大樹的頭部，這一明顯犯規的動作，被日本傳媒形容為「殺人功夫攔截」。但賽後姜至鵬卻辯稱是橋岡大樹的頭碰到他的腳。姜至鵬這番話，比他那個動作更令人譁然，卻也不讓人意外。中國隊一向視贏為唯一目的，有沒有球品，有沒有體育精神，媒體及觀眾自有判斷。有機會跟中國隊交手的運動員想必會打醒十二分精神。<br />\n<br />\n中國人每每在國際出醜，香港人特別反感，無他，擔心外國人分不清甚麼是中國人，甚麼是香港人，無端食了死貓，被歸類為同一種人。所以，香港人是最反感被視作中國人的人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不過，過去半年以來，香港人持續的抗爭運動令香港人的形象在國際視野中變得清晰，香港人爭取的五大訴求關乎民主、自由、法治以及公義。香港人不惜犧牲物質利益、押上前途和生命安全，不為私利而戰，為維護普世價值而持續作戰，令香港示威者入選2019年美國《時代》雜誌最後五強「風雲人物」。香港人能否最終獲選其實並不重要，重要的是，世界已經看到香港人是甚麼人：香港人不是中國人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">從此以後，香港人不必再苦苦地向人解釋，我們是香港人，我們跟中國人如何不一樣&hellip;&hellip; </span><br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6baa1ec63e1a936b039e75262c5805c6bbe31c","tid":1780376,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"但兒登仔話係華人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b0a51caefeb2d300a9297de6014f8a38882d9d","tid":1780376,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6be508f76acb13446b2ca6da7b4fe214b368517","tid":1780376,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"文化語言都唔同，其實好難認同自己中國人，加上咁多問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"16f64bffd5db1f8e077826f6be350a51378b55ea","tid":1780376,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"支那=侵略者、殖民者"},{"pid":"1f43423d5b31d23708fcdbd63f868eda5a432d09","tid":1780376,"uid":27871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tooQmo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tooQmo.jpg&h=effe4e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}